snippet.title: The Tall Wall Falls: The Final Defense of the Inner Gate (Trailer Video)
snippet.description: A fast-paced, physics-based, Attack on Titan inspired game. Swing around from the grapple hooks on  your swords, and take down huge enemies, before they destroy the gate! Created in 7 days for Bracky's 2020.1 Game Jam. https://request.itch.io/the-tall-wall-falls
